          "text": "Challenge: \n    \n   A Single server is not enough to store all messages in a topic\nso we Partition the topic futher so that we can store it across multiple servers \n\nSometimes we need to provide strict message order for the events that are being consumed\n    Like chat messages \n\nSolution : \n\n    Maintaing Strict Order \n    {\n      [key]: coversation_id\n        topic: messages,\n        value : {\n            message : 'Hi',\n            prev_mess_id: \" \",\n\n}, \n    timestamp : \n    [headers]\n}",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontFamily": 8,
          "textAlign": "left",
          "verticalAlign": "top",
          "containerId": null,
